{"tid":924653,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩日劇bad ending睇完令你無法釋懷一段時間？","createTime":"2018-12-02T09:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T16:29:20.000Z","uid":63113,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb03525a924cf14f9cec0f529aa43e59b0fbcd4","tid":924653,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"當年睇一公升眼淚 <br />\n<br />\n由女主知道自己有病之後套劇幾乎每集都摧淚彈嚟<br />\n<br />\n由行到講到 到慢慢跛下跛下 講嘢開始斷斷續續 由坐輪椅 到入特殊學校都改變唔到現實<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁佢仲滿懷希望日日寫文 鼓勵自己總會有未來 或者醫學昌明會有得醫<br />\n<br />\n好深刻後尾情況惡化，活動能力大減，當出去連打個公眾電話咁平常不過嘅事都打唔到，佢瞓喺病床問醫生仲有冇可能結婚，聽到呢句喺佢隔嚟嘅老竇忍唔住衝出房喊&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n最後大結局真係頂唔住 25歲就過身 之後起歌同加插真人亞也啲語錄照片<br />\n<br />\n真係一瞬間觸動咗我 過咗好耐先可以慢慢淡化嗰種遺憾同低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85eca603e6d7d66d3ed0cdb125c100f4200b8e7","tid":924653,"uid":34080,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:26:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1dac6f071525751f497412e450b4d58c7af8b9b","tid":924653,"uid":9899,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"華麗一族木村吞鎗自殺"},{"pid":"b0fb5d11b8126eff6dca8c6c1b7a50c220c3b466","tid":924653,"uid":200474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1dac6f071525751f497412e450b4d58c7af8b9b","tid":924653,"uid":9899,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"華麗一族木村吞鎗自殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完成個星期都好down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d571165c9c5e1d3fc0c94c47847d6c971c73d591","tid":924653,"uid":76632,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"在世界中心呼喚愛，去到機場&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"08a5228b1b0ed2b28efe139dcaa21994a9bfa1db","tid":924653,"uid":217318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:08:15.000Z",